---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import portrait from '../assets/tromso.jpeg';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Dr. Kees Benkendorfer"
  description="Dr. Kees Benkendorfer — personal website."
>
  <Image
    src={portrait}
    alt="Kees Benkendorfer"
    class="portrait"
    width={240}
    densities={[2]}
  />
  <h1>Home</h1>
  <p>
    I'm currently an Algo Dev Intern at Hudson River Trading, though in a (fairly recent) past life I was an experimental particle physicist working on the ATLAS experiment at CERN.
  </p>

  <h2>Brief history</h2>
  <p>
    I studied physics at Reed College (BA, 2021), then earned my PhD in
    experimental particle physics at Harvard University (2025). For nearly six years (undergrad, grad school, and a brief postdoc stint) I worked on the ATLAS experiment at CERN, where I split my time between large-scale data analysis, machine learning research, and hardware projects.
  </p>

  <p>
    My physics research revolved around the search for physics beyond the Standard Model. I developed and deployed novel unsupervised machine learning methods for anomaly detection and performed precise measurements of Standard Model processes. I also developed control and data-acquisition software for the ATLAS Inner Tracker upgrade, a new silicon tracking detector to be installed in preparation for the High-Luminosity LHC.
  </p>

  <p>
    I recently moved from academia into
    quantitative finance, and I'm now an Algo Dev Intern at HRT.
  </p>

  <p>
    For more detail, see my <a href="/experience">experience</a> and <a href="/projects">projects</a>. Please visit the <a href="/contact">contact page</a> if you would like to get in touch.
  </p>

  <p>This website is still a work in progress.</p>

  <style>
    .portrait {
      float: right;
      width: 240px;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 12px;
      margin: 0.25rem 0 1rem 1.5rem;
    }

    /* On narrow screens, stack the photo above the text and center it. */
    @media (max-width: 30rem) {
      .portrait {
        float: none;
        display: block;
        margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
